The paper proposes a solution for training a classifier using privileged information, which is a topic related to machine learning (cs.LG). The proposed algorithm is utilized for image categorization tasks, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The use of web knowledge also suggests a possible connection to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and information retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the paper involves text classification, which is a sub-topic of natural language processing (cs.CL).
